 \zeta(s) = \exp \left(\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\Lambda(n)}{\log n} n^{-s} \right)
\zeta(s)
p^k
p
\Lambda(n)=\left\{\begin{array}{rl} \log p & \mbox{if}\ n=p^k\\ 0 & \mbox{else} \end{array} \right.
\log(\zeta (s))=\sum\frac{\Lambda(n)}{\log n}n^{-s}\\ \Rightarrow \zeta(s)=\exp\left(\sum\frac{\Lambda(n)}{\log n}n^{-s}\right)  \Box 
